Body: Description: Does not seem that the file system monitoring is working properly. Some permissions seem to be off when you compare it to the folder permissions on the server.
Next Steps Updated: If the scan fails with the same error, "T2 database does not match the T1 database," I will delete the T2 and rerun the Permission scan
What We've Learned Updated: Some permissions are off when compared to the folder permissions on the server because the Bulk Import is not working as it should.
